net.nemerosa.ontrack.extension.issues.model

Class IssueServiceConfigurationRepresentation

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.nemerosa.ontrack.extension.issues.model.IssueServiceConfigurationRepresentation

  • public class IssueServiceConfigurationRepresentation
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to represent an IssueServiceConfiguration to a client. The proposed id is composed from the service id and from the configuration name, separated by //.
    See Also:
    IssueServiceConfigurationIdentifier
